        "ri-body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One of the quieter corners of the villa. In the morning the light is cool and filtered; by four in the afternoon the terrace is a warm pool of gold. A king bed with hand-washed linen, a small writing desk by the window, hand-thrown ceramic tiles we commissioned from a potter in Lefkes, and nothing else. No television, no minibar.</p>",
