            "text": "Who it's best for.",
            "size": "4xl",
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "gk-body-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Honeymoon couples and slow travelers who want a real stone terrace without leaving the room. The east-facing orientation means soft morning light through the jasmine and strong afternoon warmth on the terrace — ideal for guests who like to start the day quiet and read outdoors in the late afternoon.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "left"
          }
        }
